race.comment: IMPRISONMENT (3) has a strong record here with seven wins and a minor from 12 starts. Was out of placings last time (25.84) at Q Lakeside in a Grade 5, finishing fifth and beaten 6 lengths. Looks a key chance on best form. WAIKARIE VENOM (2) had a wide draw last time when running fourth (25.75) over 457m at Q Lakeside in a Grade 5. Form here at the trip sound including five wins. Cannot be taken lightly. RIDING SOLO (6) scored by 4.5 lengths last time (23.82) in a Free For All over 407m at this track. Looks suited here and can measure up. CORONATION DAY (8) put a gap on his rivals last start. Big chance on that form.
